---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Public Works Digital - Open Source Government Technology"
  description="Public Works Digital - Building transparent, open-source software for government. We create civic technology that serves the public interest."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Government software built in the open</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        We build transparent, accountable technology for cities and their citizens.
        No vendor lock-in. No black boxes. Just honest, open-source software that serves the public good.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/about" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More</a>
        <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-secondary">View Our Work</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="features-content">
      <h2>A new model for civic technology</h2>
      <div class="feature-grid">
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Open Source by Default</h3>
          <p>
            Every line of code we write is public. Citizens can inspect, verify, and contribute
            to the software that governs their daily lives. No secrets, no surprises.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>Professional Support</h3>
          <p>
            Enterprise-grade reliability with dedicated support, training, and maintenance.
            We're not just developersâ€”we're partners in your digital transformation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature">
          <h3>True Ownership</h3>
          <p>
            Your city owns the code. Forever. Switch vendors, self-host, or modify as needed.
            We eliminate vendor lock-in and put control back in public hands.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="problem">
    <div class="problem-content">
      <h2>The crisis in government technology</h2>
      <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">$521B</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Annual government procurement waste</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">78%</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Potential cost savings with open source</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <span class="stat-number">Zero</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Citizens who can audit proprietary systems</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="problem-text">
        Cities are trapped by vendors who charge extortionate fees, deliver broken systems,
        and disappear when problems arise. Meanwhile, citizens have no visibility into the
        technology making decisions about their lives. <strong>It's time for a change.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <div class="cta-content">
      <h2>Ready to transform your city's technology?</h2>
      <p>
        Join forward-thinking municipalities building transparent, accountable government
        for the 21st century.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Start the Conversation</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero Section */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gray-50) 0%, var(--gray-100) 100%);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  /* Features Section */
  .features {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .features-content {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--gray-900);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .feature p {
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  /* Problem Section */
  .problem {
    background: var(--gray-50);
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
  }

  .problem-content {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .problem-text {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--gray-600);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .problem-text strong {
    color: var(--gray-900);
  }

  /* CTA Section */
  .cta {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: var(--gray-900);
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-content {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta h2 {
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--gray-200);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .stats {
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .stat-number {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
